### Docling service — examples for VS Code REST Client
### Variables: set apiKey to match DOCLING_API_KEY in your `.env`.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@apiKey = local-demo-change-me

### Health check (no API key required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### For multipart upload, use the shell script (recommended):
###   ./scripts/demo-convert.sh samples/local-demo.pdf
###
### Or curl:
### curl -sS -X POST "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/convert" \
###   -H "X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}" \
###   -F "file=@samples/local-demo.pdf" \
###   -F "output_format=markdown" \
###   -F "ocr_enabled=true"
